product_name: Omega Pacific 7/16'' Mod D Quik-Lok Carabiner - Steel
long_description: The heavy-duty Omega Pacific 7/16 in. Mod D Quik-Lok carabiner is suitable for setting up top-rope anchors, belay anchors and rigging for a rescue. Modified D-shape provides excellent handling for all-around use. Steel is heat treated and plated for superb corrosion resistance. Quik-Lok autolocking gate mechanism ensures fast, reliable locking.
short_description: The heavy-duty Omega Pacific 7/16 in. Mod D Quik-Lok carabiner is suitable for setting up top-rope anchors, belay anchors and rigging for a rescue.
